Compilers :
	In c++ the compiler is g++ .
	For Compiling g++ filename.cpp .(For direct compilation)
	Compilation Stages :
	1 . Prepprocessing : converts source code to intermediate code 
			cpp -o main.i main.c
	2 . Compiling : converts intermediate code to assembly code 
			g++ -S main.i
	3 . Assembler : converts assembly code to object code 
			as -o main.o main.s
	4 . Linking and Loading : generation of machine code 
			g++ -o main.out main.o
